#### **Day 3-4: Violation Detection Engine**
**File**: `lib/copy-audit.ts` (new)
```typescript
interface Violation {
  type: 'passive-voice' | 'long-sentence' | 'jargon' | 'spelling-inconsistency';
  severity: 'high' | 'medium' | 'low';
  text: string;
  suggestion: string;
  page: string;
